LEASE COMMITMENTS

CERTAIN NONCANCELABLE LEASES ARE CLASSIFIED AS CAPITAL LEASES, AND THE LEASED

ASSETS ARE INCLUDED AS PART OF PROPERTIES, PLANT AND EQUIPMENT, AT COST. SUCH

