PROCESSING EQUIPMENT, SERVICE STATIONS, AND OTHER FACILITIES. OTHER LEASES ARE

CLASSIFIED AS OPERATING LEASES AND ARE NOT CAPITALIZED. THE PAYMENTS ON SUCH

LEASES ARE RECORDED AS EXPENSE. DETAILS OF THE CAPITALIZED LEASED ASSETS ARE AS

