STOCKHOLDERS OF RECORD NUMBERED APPROXIMATELY 247,000. THROUGH OCTOBER 9, 2001,

THE COMMON STOCK TRADED UNDER THE NAME OF CHEVRON CORPORATION (TRADING SYMBOL.

CHV).

THERE ARE NO RESTRICTIONS ON THE COMPANYS ABILITY TO PAY DIVIDENDS.

